<slide title="SQLite Disadvantages">

<image filename="stats.jpg" align="center" />

<list fontsize="3.5em">
	<bullet fontsize="4em">It's Slow</bullet>
		<bullet marginleft="1.5em">Locks whole file for writing.</bullet>
		<bullet marginleft="1.5em">No caching mechanism of it's own.</bullet>

	<bullet fontsize="4em">Limited</bullet>
		<bullet marginleft="1.5em">Database size restricted to 2GB in most cases.</bullet>
		<bullet marginleft="1.5em">Not fully SQL92 compliant.</bullet>
		<bullet marginleft="1.5em">Not very scalable.</bullet>
</list>
</slide>
